org.apache.jackrabbit.webdav.lock
Interface ActiveLock

All Superinterfaces:
XmlSerializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractActiveLock
public interface ActiveLock
extends XmlSerializable

ActiveLock encapsulates the lock information for a DavResource.
